All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Object>, InternalElement, Locatable
public class GenericRecursionValue
extends GenericActionValue

Element to set the semantic value to a list of actions. This element sets the semantic value to a pair, whose value is an action that produces a generic node. The generic node's children are a production's component expressions, with the action's argument being the first child.
